description: Selina Hospitality PLC operates as a hospitality company to address the needs of travelers. The company offers accommodation solutions, including luxury lofts to comfortable suites, micro-rooms, and hammocks that suit high-end travelers, backpackers, solo explorers, and groups. Its portfolio includes approximately 163 open or secured properties across 25 countries and 6 continents. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
